<h1>Stadlg.ini file reference</h1>
<p>File Date: 2020-12-10</p>

<p>File has a number of sections, each section defines a report-layout.
The name of the section identifies the report, as referenced from starep.ini and from the refrep table
through calls to the statusindex-functions.  </p>

There are a number of entries, for fields, pushbuttons, parameters, and other control info.  

$param name=string
Special case: $param deltacol=

$postprocess=

Table Field Funcion=width (legend) (alias) 

Special fields:
$leaf=width (legend) (alias)
$Trunk
$Branches

Other specialties:
$omit=
$title=
$head=
$foot=
$levelfields=
$before=
$after=
$leaf=


Select and FORALL in call0013.html
$select lilprint Print!=4 (Print Y/N) I:3 Y N #carrier RECEIVED PrintOut
Print!=FORALL2 0 (Printe Selected Records) CL_Print

LCXCALL Buttons in call3206 Section 4
$button FIELDACT=LCXCALL 1 (Assign field activity) SIFieldAct conserialcol+treelinecol

QREPORT buttons info in call0010.html and qreportini.html
$button CALCX=QREPORT1 1 (Q status) QASHREP S:3,4 L:16 G:21 T:31






